and grating.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_100cf5d6-36fd-4e9e-bdf6-26534b00555d" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c06cf6f3-53ca-4524-b9ce-326451dfe1e7">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>In a Class 9c building, the following facilities must be provided for every 60 beds or part thereof on each storey containing <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1437_4.0.0.xml#_071db02d-667d-447e-9f1e-8de8c46b9e0e" id="_4f13bef5-cd5d-4076-b19d-412219b14f16" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">resident use areas</xref>:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_3e57f11b-63b0-4236-9ee7-27222dfc4741">One slop-hopper or other device other than a water closet pan or urinal for the safe handling and disposal of liquid and solid wastes with a flushing apparatus, tap and grating.</li><li id="_f860d00e-1d95-42be-8854-2fd907bbffe6">An appliance for the disinfection of pans or an adequate means to dispose of receptacles.</li></ol></subclause></clause>